<Author>Taster
<Content>Nice Hotel in Hip Area My daughter and I shared a twin room for 5 nights. It was rather small, but clean and comfortable. The only problem was that it faced the front street and was quite noisy, as taxi stand is below. The windows blocked the noise, but needed to be open, as it was hot.We asked for a room facing the back, which would have been nice, but they were full. Lovely hotel, generous breakfast, nice solarium/ garden area. Staff very friendly and helpful. We will return, and ask for a back room. 
